  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to have a basic CLI to interact with a running Status instance. First step is to define what we plan to implement.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\nThis [proposal](https://gist.github.com/jeluard/7611c538887565a9c16429522bdeb8c5) can be used as a basis for discussion.\r\n\r\nPlan is to:\r\n\r\n* align with Embark and others DApps devs needs\r\n* publish proposal to discuss to engage with the community\r\n* finalize the proposal",
